  Title: Roblox World Zero XP Stats

  Description: This program displays:

  1.
  The amount of xp required to advance
  to the next Level

  2.Total XP per any given Level, XP Per 
  Enemy, Total Amount of Enemies Per Level,
  Total Xp including Bosses.
  
*****************************************/
																										

// Text Colors

/* BLACK 0			 * DARKGREY 8
 * BLUE 1			 * LIGHTBLUE 9
 * GREEN 2			 * LIGHTGREEN 10
 * CYAN 3			 * LIGHTCYAN 11
